es - ''Rites of Chaos''\n* [[Deep Purple]] - ''[[Perfect Strangers (album)|Perfect Strangers]]''\n* Der Kaiser \u2013 ''Vautours''\n* [[Destruction (band)|Destruction]] - ''[[Sentence of Death]]'' (EP)\n* [[Paul Di%27Anno|Di'Anno]] - ''[[Di%27Anno (album)|Di'Anno]]''\n* [[Dio (band)|Dio]] - ''[[The Last in Line]]''\n* [[Dokken]] - ''[[Tooth and Nail (Dokken album)|Tooth and Nail]]''\n* Elessar - ''Defy the King'' (EP)\n* [[Earthshaker (band)|Earthshaker]] - ''Fugitive''\n* Earthshaker - ''Midnight Flight''\n* Eric Steel - ''Eric Steel''\n* [[Europe (band)|Europe]] - ''[[Wings of Tomorrow]]''\n* Evil - ''Evil's Message'' (EP)\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]] - ''[[Violence & Force]]''\n* Faithful Breath - ''Gold 'n' Glory''\n* [[Fastway (band)|Fastway]] - ''[[All Fired Up (Fastway album)|All Fired Up]]''\n* [[Fates Warning]] - ''[[Night on Br\u00f6cken]]''\n* Force \u2013 ''Set Me Free''\n* [[Ezo (band)|Flatbacker]] - ''Minagoroshi''\n* [[Lita Ford]] - ''[[Dancin' on the Edge]]''\n* [[Rhett Forrester]] - ''Gone with the Wind''\n* Gilgamesj - ''Take One'' (EP)\n* Glory Bells - ''Century Rendezvous''\n* Gotham City - ''The Unknown'' \n* [[Grave Digger (band)|Grave Digger]] - ''[[Heavy Metal Breakdown]]''\n* Graven Image - ''People in Hell Want Ice Water'' (EP)\n* Gravestone \u2013 ''Victim of Chains''\n* [[Great White]] - ''[[Great White (album)|Great White]]''\n* Griffin - ''Flight of the Griffin''\n* [[Sammy Hagar]] - ''[[VOA (album)|VOA]]''\n* Hammer \u2013 ''Contract with Hell''\n* Hammerhead - ''Heart Made of Steel'' (EP)\n* Hammers Rule - ''Show No Mercy''\n* [[Hanoi Rocks]] - ''[[All Those Waisted Years]]'' (live)\n* Hanoi Rocks - ''[[Two Steps from the Move]]''\n* [[Hawaii (band)|Hawaii]] - ''[[Loud, Wild and Heavy]]'' (EP)\n* [[Hazzard]] - ''Hazzard''\n* H-Bomb - ''Attaque''\n* [[Helix (band)|Helix]] - ''[[Walkin' the Razor's Edge]]''\n* Hellanbach - ''The Big H''\n* [[Hellhammer]] - ''[[Apocalyptic Raids]]'' (EP)\n* Hellion (NY) - ''Dangerous Maneuvers''\n* [[He